{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T12:34:01.043660Z", "created_at": "Wed Nov 07 15:51:14 +0000 2018", "created_at_iso": "2018-11-07T15:51:14Z", "created_at_ts": 1541605874, "display_name": "Emily Randall", "handle": "emilyrandallwa", "id": "1060197996783034368", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DraUdNTXgAEtByZ.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 8, \"reply_count\": 3, \"like_count\": 38, \"quote_count\": 2, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "As we expected, this race is really close. We are currently leading by 474 votes with 50.6% — with LOTS of votes to be counted. Because of your hard work, our GOTV operation was strong 💪🏽 and we’re looking forward to more Dem votes showing up in the coming day’s returns. https://t.co/CblUls5qZb", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "EmilyRandallWA"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T12:34:01.043660Z", "created_at": "Wed Nov 07 15:52:27 +0000 2018", "created_at_iso": "2018-11-07T15:52:27Z", "created_at_ts": 1541605947, "display_name": "Emily Randall", "handle": "emilyrandallwa", "id": "1060198302086393856", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 2, \"reply_count\": 1, \"like_count\": 26, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I’m proud of what we have done. We kept our campaign about community, rising above the outside special interest $$$ that paid for negative attack after negative attack. We stayed focused on mobilizing grassroots volunteers, talking to our neighbors about real issues. Thank you 💙", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "EmilyRandallWA"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T12:33:54.893551Z", "created_at": "Wed Nov 07 18:05:26 +0000 2018", "created_at_iso": "2018-11-07T18:05:26Z", "created_at_ts": 1541613926, "display_name": "Elissa Slotkin", "handle": "elissaslotkin", "id": "1060231769436446720", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DrazKO4WsAAlReA.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 107, \"reply_count\": 86, \"like_count\": 1074, \"quote_count\": 32, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "Thank you again to everyone who was a part of this grassroots-powered campaign. The full results are; we received 172,878 votes to Rep. Bishop's 159,804. Dave &amp; I are enjoying a day at home -- the dogs are the happiest constituents because they get a proper romp around the farm! https://t.co/kf09k4t4jo", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "ElissaSlotkin"}
